1
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:29,850
♪Our tangled destiny
has trapped my heart in this life♪

2
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Will I see you again in the next life♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:43,500
♪Keep a piece of peach blossom
to remember the past and say goodbye♪

4
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:49,920
♪But I still miss you
with tears in my eyes♪

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:57,250
♪Dig a hole, plant a tree, but the leaves
and flowers remind me of our past♪

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:03,710
♪Sow the seeds of love,
but they bloom on the wrong path♪

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:11,060
♪Move on, let go,
forget everything about you♪

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:18,220
♪Flowers fall on the road
where I fell in love with you♪

9
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:37,660
=Stolen Love=

10
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,700
=Episode 5=

11
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,680
You came here alone.

12
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:53,080
Do you really think
I wouldn't dare to kill you?

13
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,920
I'll stay loyal to the Zhou Family

14
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,360
even if I'm dead.

15
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,400
I'll die for them

16
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,520
without regrets.

17
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,170
Lu Yunxi!

18
00:02:07,170 --> 00:02:09,720
♪Sad songs echo in the air♪

19
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,080
Did you forget

20
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,440
my aunt,

21
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,680
your mother-in-law,

22
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,440
forced my father

23
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:22,840
to sell you to a dying old man
as a concubine?

24
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:25,520
♪We said goodbye♪

25
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,240
I was exiled to the frontier

26
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,920
on our wedding day.

27
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,210
Did you forget that?

28
00:02:33,210 --> 00:02:35,170
♪My cries♪

29
00:02:35,290 --> 00:02:36,910
♪And sighs♪

30
00:02:37,250 --> 00:02:39,910
♪Are buried in the snow♪

31
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,760
General,

32
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,400
things have changed.

33
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,160
If you fight against the Zhou Family,

34
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,200
you'll be my enemy.

35
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,430
♪Broke my heart♪

36
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:56,480
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

37
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,310
♪Even your name♪

38
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:03,790
♪Is a forbidden word♪

39
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:06,200
One day, I'll kill everyone
in the Zhou Family,

40
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:11,520
including that man's son.

41
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:17,280
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

42
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:21,840
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

43
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,120
(Chuyi,)

44
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,320
(please don't blame me.)

45
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,600
(As long as Che and you can survive,)

46
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,840
(I'm willing to do anything,)

47
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,880
(even if I have to die.)

48
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,840
This secret room

49
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,520
is filled with poison gas,

50
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:46,200
and only the method

51
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,320
passed down by generations
of ladies in charge

52
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,840
can ensure safe entry.

53
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,720
Even His Majesty

54
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,320
can't get out alive

55
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:55,320
if he breaks in without guidance.

56
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:58,420
I wanted to lure that idiot in,

57
00:03:58,420 --> 00:03:59,740
(Crown Prince)
but

58
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,360
you used Lu Yunxi's strategy instead.

59
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,880
If he died in your mansion,

60
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:06,160
you'd be responsible.

61
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,760
Your servants and followers
are everywhere.

62
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,600
We'll find another way.

63
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,880
If we can hit him hard

64
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,680
without killing him,

65
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,560
it'll be much better.

66
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:22,240
He has to pay for

67
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,160
what he did today.

68
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,240
Tomorrow,

69
00:04:25,250 --> 00:04:26,880
I'll ask the ministers to report him.

70
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,120
As for Lu Yunxi,

71
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,680
even if Xiao Chuyi doesn't kill her,

72
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,760
we can't keep her.

73
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:38,000
Xiao Chuyi cares about her so much.

74
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,760
It's not a bad thing for us.

75
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,160
If she's willing to take our side,

76
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,400
we'll keep her.

77
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:55,140
(Zhou's Mansion)

78
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:10,080
Lady Lu, the 27th wife of the heir

79
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,360
of the Zhou Family,

80
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:15,040
and Zhou Che, the 28th heir
of the Zhou Family,

81
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,320
are included in the family tree.

82
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:20,600
You shall abide by the family rules,

83
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,160
cultivate outstanding talents,

84
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,160
bless future generations,

85
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,040
respect the ancestors
in the family tree,

86
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,880
and make the family thrive.

87
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,040
Good girl.

88
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,120
The child

89
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:39,040
and you must survive.

90
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:42,280
I've chosen a name.

91
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,640
It's Che.

92
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,240
Che.

93
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,800
I hope Che

94
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:56,120
can live a bright
[*Che: clear and bright]

95
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,960
and dignified life.

96
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:03,540
(Zhou Che, courtesy name Liangshan,
pseudonym Jinghu)

97
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,120
(Mother,)

98
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,920
(I will survive.)

99
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,160
(I won't die)

100
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:31,240
(until I complete the mission
you left me.)

101
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,080
You abducted someone else's bride,

102
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,600
set fire to the ancestral hall,

103
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,240
and defied the elder.

104
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,600
My court is filled with

105
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,720
impeachment memorials from the censors.

106
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:21,600
If you hadn't fought against the enemy

107
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,400
and made great contributions,

108
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,800
I wouldn't go easy on you.

109
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,160
The censors are so biased against me.

110
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,320
They should impeach Yanyu
for stealing Yunxi.

111
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,160
Nonsense!

112
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,760
How dare you argue with me?

113
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,440
Your Majesty, I'm begging you.

114
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:44,720
I'm willing to give up
my titles, assets, and salaries

115
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:47,440
to get my wife Lu Yunxi back.

116
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,680
Your Majesty, I beg for your permission.

117
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:54,800
Xiao Chuyi!

118
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,400
Father,

119
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,720
Grand General said something wrong

120
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,840
on impulse.

121
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,960
Please don't punish him.

122
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,360
On impulse?

123
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,640
He's obviously threatening me
with his merits.

124
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,840
This is outrageous!

125
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,680
How dare you joke about

126
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,720
the rewards I granted you?

127
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,480
I'm deadly serious.

128
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,960
I just can't accept the fact

129
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,000
that he stole my wife.

130
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,120
I fought for the country and people

131
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,120
on the frontier

132
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,160
and nearly died!

133
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:23,200
In the end,
I couldn't even protect my wife.

134
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:26,600
How am I supposed to be a real man?

135
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,600
Xiao Chuyi,

136
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,760
are you starting a rebellion?

137
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,560
Father!

138
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,840
He has no such intention.

139
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:43,280
He's just too aggrieved.

140
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,200
Father,

141
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,320
given his great contributions,

142
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,240
please don't punish him.

143
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,040
Father, your health

144
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,000
is the priority.

145
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,080
I'll definitely

146
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,880
persuade him.

147
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,920
Chuyi.

148
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,120
I had no such intention.

149
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:02,320
He should be grateful

150
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,600
that I didn't blame him
for deceiving me.

151
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,520
The title of Honorary Lady

152
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,880
is for your wife

153
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,480
instead of someone else's wife.

154
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,320
Lu Yunxi is my wife!

155
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,880
I've never died in battle

156
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:25,160
or agreed to divorce her.

157
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,080
Guards!

158
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:33,160
Get him out of here and hit his back

159
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,120
30 times with a stick!

160
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,160
Father!

161
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,600
He's got old wounds. I'm afraid...

162
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:39,080
Your Majesty, I beg for your permission

163
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:40,640
to get my wife back!

164
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,800
50 times!

165
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,760
Your Majesty, I beg for your permission

166
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,360
- to get my wife back!
- Father!

167
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,840
Your Majesty,

168
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,520
- 80 times!
- I beg for your permission

169
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,560
to get my wife back!

170
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:55,280
Your Majesty, I beg for your permission

171
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,400
to get my wife back!

172
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:12,160
Your Majesty,

173
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,400
please give her back to me...

174
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,880
Lu Yunxi

175
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:19,160
- voluntarily joined their family tree.
- Your Majesty,

176
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,760
- Is it worth it?
- please give her back to me...

177
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,400
Your Majesty...

178
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:29,640
Please give her back to me...

179
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,000
Mother,

180
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,840
General Xiao was hit 80 times
with a stick

181
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,320
and passed out.

182
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,440
Mother, don't worry.

183
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,440
I'll ask the imperial doctor
to check on him.

184
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,840
I heard

185
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,000
he wanted to give up all his merits

186
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,280
for Sister

187
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,320
and provoked His Majesty.

188
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,560
He was still begging His Majesty

189
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,840
to give Sister back to him
when they hit him.

190
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,080
No wonder

191
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,720
she's the most beautiful woman
in the capital.

192
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:43,960
Stay out of my sight, all of you.

193
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:56,480
Why are you still here?

194
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,200
Mother,

195
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,240
you asked my father

196
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:01,640
to work with the censors
to impeach Chuyi.

197
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,800
It really worked.

198
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:04,840
Your father and you

199
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:09,360
will be rewarded.

200
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,120
Hurry!

201
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,200
Prince Su has said

202
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,320
if anything happens to him,

203
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,240
he'll kill all of you!

204
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,200
Hurry!

205
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,560
The old wounds haven't healed.

206
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:25,600
Can he survive this?

207
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,080
He's had a fever for 12 hours.

208
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:27,920
I'm afraid he can't.

209
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,320
You're so careless.

210
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,600
The doctor said

211
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,920
the fever was caused by his rage.

212
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,520
You're the best doctor.

213
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,040
Just tell me the truth.

214
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,600
How's General Xiao?

215
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:42,000
I've used the most effective medicine.

216
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,960
If his high fever persists,

217
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,680
I won't be able to save him.

218
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:17,750
♪My cries♪

219
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,490
♪And sighs♪

220
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:22,770
♪Are buried in the snow♪

221
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,470
♪Horses run♪

222
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:27,150
♪Into my dreams♪

223
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:30,900
♪And I see you again♪

224
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:33,170
♪You left♪

225
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,010
♪Broke my heart♪

226
00:13:35,180 --> 00:13:39,060
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

227
00:13:39,660 --> 00:13:41,890
♪Even your name♪

228
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:46,370
♪Is a forbidden word♪

229
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:50,470
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

230
00:13:50,470 --> 00:13:54,720
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

231
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:58,170
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

232
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:02,120
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

233
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:05,900
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

234
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:09,780
♪Only to call your name again♪

235
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:13,830
♪For it's the only thing♪

236
00:14:14,110 --> 00:14:17,840
♪I'll never forget♪

237
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:21,360
