238
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:25,670
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

239
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:29,510
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

240
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,710
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

241
00:14:33,830 --> 00:14:36,890
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

242
00:14:36,890 --> 00:14:40,830
♪Only to call your name again♪

243
00:14:41,170 --> 00:14:44,540
♪For it's the only thing♪

244
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:48,840
♪I'll never forget♪

245
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:56,080
♪Till the day that I die♪
